info.name: Classic Chicken
info.description: Grilled, juicy chicken breast paired with pulled mashed potatoes, topped with luscious mushroom sauce.

info.name: Dynamite Shrimps
info.description: Succulent shrimp, delicately coated in flour and fried to perfection, and drenched in our signature dynamite sauce.

info.name: Fettuccine Pasta
info.description: Al dente pasta generously coated in a creamy chicken-mushroom sauce, seasoned with fragrant parsley, parmesan cheese, and a touch of salt and pepper.

info.name: Beef Kakkaroti
info.description: A blend of exotic spices, tender cuts of beef and a fiery kick from fresh green chillies.

info.name: Cheese Chilli Fries
info.description: Crispy breaded chicken topped over golden French fries, smothered in melted cheddar cheese and fiery dynamite sauce. Finished with some chilli flakes, fresh spring onions, and red chilli.

info.name: Chicken Breakfast Burrito
info.description: Vibrant spring onions dance alongside fluffy scrambled eggs, all coming together in a soft tortilla wrap. Drizzled with guacamole paste and garnished with fresh coriander leaves.

info.name: Grilled Chicken With Hummus
info.description: Tender chicken slices, grilled to perfection, served top a bed of creamy hummus, infused with the richness of olive oil.

info.name: Oriental Rice With Beef
info.description: Fragrant basmati rice cooked with a blend of seven spices, enriched with the savory depth of chicken broth and a touch of butter for richness. Topped with shawarma beef and tahini.

info.name: Schezwan Chicken
info.description: Tender breaded chicken, coated in crispy panko crumbs and seasoned to perfection with salt and black pepper powder, meets the cool crunch of coleslaw.

info.name: Sora Pathiri With Chicken Ghee Roast
info.description: Soft, delicate layers, each carrying the essence of spices and coconut, paired perfectly with the rich Chicken Ghee Roast. An authentic Malabar experience

info.name: Avacado Egg Toast
info.description: Fluffy poached eggs and melted feta cheese topped with creamy guacamole and drizzled with hollandaise sauce for a savory morning indulgence.

info.name: Break Burrito
info.description: Vibrant spring onions dance alongside fluffy scrambled eggs, all coming together in a soft tortilla wrap. Drizzled with guacamole paste and garnished with fresh coriander leaves.

info.name: Chicken Quesadilia
info.description: Succulent chicken mix, bursting with savory goodness, is wrapped in a soft tortilla along with a generous layer of melted cheddar cheese.

info.name: Grilled Chicken Roll
info.description: Indulge in our mouth-watering Chicken Wrap, featuring tender chicken in a soft tortilla with garlic or spicy mayo.

info.name: Mexican Wrap
info.description: A savory mix of tender chicken, black beans, and gooey mozzarella cheese wrapped in a tortilla wrap. The crispiness of tortilla and delicate cheese is a bite that you can't miss.

info.name: Mosakhan Chicken Roll
info.description: A tantalizing fusion of tender chicken, caramelized onions, and fragrant spices, all wrapped up in a warm, fluffy roll.

info.name: Seafood Wrap
info.description: A refreshing blend of shrimp and squid. Tossed with diced onion, garlic, and a hint of green chilli for a burst of flavour. A true Malabar and Goan fusion.

info.name: Beef Sandwich
info.description: Tender marinated beef grilled with onions, green capsicum, and garlic, then layered with cheddar and mozzarella cheese on freshly toasted bread

info.name: Chicken Sandwich
info.description: Featuring tender chicken and crisp lettuce nestled between layers of melted cheddar and mozzarella cheese on freshly toasted bread

info.name: Veg Sandwich
info.description: A delightful medley of fresh, colorful veggies layered between soft bread slices.

info.name: Sago Pudding
info.description: Soft sago pearls simmered in creamy milk, sweetened with rich jaggery and coconut milk.

info.name: Banana Foster
info.description: A warm, toasted bun layered with caramelized bananas and a dollop of velvety ice cream.

info.name: Garanola Karikku
info.description: Layering crunchy granola with ripe mango and tender karikku (tender coconut) pieces. Drizzled with creamy milk and a touch of sugar for sweetness, each layer is topped with a scoop of ice cream and a decadent swirl of caramel sauce.

info.name: Avocado Shake
info.description: Blending ripe avocado with rich milk and a hint of sugar for sweetness. Served chilled with a scoop of velvety ice cream, it's a treat that combines the creamy goodness of avocado with the refreshing coolness of ice cream.

info.name: Beetroot Shake
info.description: Blending the earthy sweetness of beetroot with the nuttiness of almonds.

info.name: Green Mango Shake
info.description: Made with ripe mangoes and a secret natural ingredient filled with nutrition for it's green colour. Blended to creamy perfection, it's the perfect pick-me-up for any time of day.

info.name: Karikku Mango Shake
info.description: Blending ripe mangoes and tender karikku (tender coconut) with creamy milk and a touch of sugar for sweetness. Topped with a scoop of velvety ice cream, it's a tropical delight!

info.name: Pina Colada
info.description: Blending sweet pineapple and tender coconut with creamy milk and a touch of sugar for sweetness. Topped with a scoop of refreshing ice cream, it's a luscious combination of tropical flavours that will transport you to paradise.

info.name: Strawberry Shake
info.description: Blending fresh strawberries with creamy milk and a touch of sugar for sweetness. Topped with a scoop of indulgent ice cream.

info.name: Teeta Lime Regular
info.description: Juicy raw mangoes blended with fresh mint leaves, tangy lime juice.

info.name: Green Apple Mojito
info.description: Tangy lime and fresh mint meet fizzy soda water, with a hint of Green apple flavor and sugar syrup, served over ice for a refreshing pick-me-up.

info.name: Passion Fruit Mojito
info.description: Tangy lime and fresh mint meet fizzy soda water, with a hint of Passion fruit flavor and sugar syrup, served over ice for a refreshing pick-me-up.

info.name: Blue Berry Mojito
info.description: Tangy lime and fresh mint meet fizzy soda water, with a hint of Blueberry flavor and sugar syrup, served over ice for a refreshing pick-me-up.
